title: Remodeled W Bloomington 3br 2 bath
posting_body: ['Available Oct 1st 2022', 'Excellent location!', 'Beautiful West Bloomington home in quiet neighborhood.', 'Near Penn and Old Shakopee Rd.', '35W freeway access just seconds away.', 'Many restaurants, and shopping nearby.', 'Nine mile creek, parks, and walking paths.', 'Great neighbors with children.', 'Open floor plan.', 'Renovated home includes, remodeled kitchen, with Cambria quarts counter tops, kitchen cabinets, with slow close doors, and drawers, big pullout drawers, spice pull out drawer, and lighting under cabinets, top of the line LG stainless steel appliances, gas stove with 2 ovens, exhaust fan vented outside above stove, tiled heated floor in kitchen, new kitchen, bath window, and in dinette.', '2 Bathrooms: One full bath up, and 3/4 down with shower, both totally redone from tiled floors, tiled walls, sinks with cabinet, hardware, lighting and new main bath window all recently professionally updated.', 'Hardwood floors throughout main level with wood-burning fireplace in living room, and another wood-burning fireplace in lower level, Radon Mitigation System, Water Softener, New 100 Amp service with new panel, and new electrical outlets, switches throughout home, also canned lighting in living room.', 'Built in speakers in living room/kitchen area, New roof, gutters, and fascia replaced Nov 2021', 'Large fenced in yard,', 'Double Garage, Non Smoking Home Tenants responsible for all utilities, including snow removal and lawn care', 'NO CATS', 'NOT APPROVED FOR SECTION 8 VOUCHERS', '1 year lease minimum', 'Household income needs to be 3X greater then rent Background and credit check will be done 45.00 app fee per adult', 'DEPOSIT is same amount as the rent', 'Contact Sonia for private showing']
